<br />Yet hobbyists port FCEUX and Snes9x to every newly cracked console as it appears. It appears to be the "hello world" of homebrew. So why <em>shouldn't</em> a publisher port its classic games to every console in an effort to satisfy players' desires before the ROM pirates do?

		

