		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />The good thing is that nobody forces you to buy remakes (at least for now while games are still distributed in physical media), if you don't like them, just don't buy them. You can't really expect a company to acknowledge that a game can already be played on a system through piracy on a certain platform and use that as a reason to not release a remake of said game on said platform.

		

